name: EGO_DEATH
description:
EGO_DEATH has a different meaning than the one portrayed by Joseph Campbell. The meaning behind this artwork is meant to show a metamorphosis in terms of evolution. Even if technology takes apart, we constantly go back to our true nature. In this manner, the only chance is not to take a side, but to embrace and use both sides, natural and artificial, in order to find balance.
